messageBody:
Hi,
I have a question if I have a method in a class which calls 2 other methods of the same class. How do unit test this method.How do I check if its passing correct parameters to other methods. eg
method XYZ()
{
int x;
int y;
aa(x);
bb(y);
}
aa() ,bb(),XYZ() are all methods of the same class.
I can unit test aa() and bb()in isolation but how do I test that methos XYZ is passing correct values tp aa and bb
